Facilyn: The gut feel check builds on the mental picture that has formed after passing through all the other checks. It asks about your feelings and effects on the greater whole:

Facilyn: "How do we feel about this action now? Will it lead to the quality of life we desire? Will it adversely affect the lives of others?"

