Facilyn: This check asks about your *intuition* rather than what you *think*. It connects directly to the values in your quality of life statement.

Facilyn: Even if an action passes all other checks, you might reject it if it doesn't feel right. Conversely, you might proceed with a flawed action if your gut says it's necessary, now knowing the negative consequences and aware you must mitigate the downsides.

